# VNRequestTrackingLevel.fast

**Case**

Tracking level that favors speed over location accuracy.

## Declaration

```swift
case fast
```

## Discussion

This is the default option used by trackers.

## Enumeration Cases

- **VNRequestTrackingLevel.accurate**: Tracking level that favors location accuracy over speed.
